<div class="card">
    <h1>Cat Care 101 🧶</h1>
    <p>Thinking of bringing a cat home? Be sure to keep these tips in mind:</p>
    
    <ul class="adopt-list">
        <li><strong>Hydration:</strong> Cats often prefer running water, so consider getting a pet fountain.</li>
        <li><strong>Scratching:</strong> Provide plenty of scratching posts so they don't use (destroy) your furniture.</li>
        <li><strong>Playtime:</strong> Spend at least 15 minutes a day playing with them so they stay healthy.</li>
        <li><strong>Love:</strong> Build a strong bond by being actively connected to your cat.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

